<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <title>Recuperação de Senha do ${sistema}</title>
    <!--
     The style block is collapsed on page load to save you some scrolling.
     Postmark automatically inlines all CSS properties for maximum email client
     compatibility. You can just update styles here, and Postmark does the rest.
     -->
</head>
<body style="background-color: #F2F4F6; color: #74787E; height: 100%; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; width: 100% !important;">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="email-wrapper" style="background-color: #F2F4F6; margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%;" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td class="container" style="clear: both !important; margin: 0 auto !important; max-width: 600px !important; word-break: break-word;" width="600">
            <div class="content" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 600px; padding: 20px;">
                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="email-content" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%;" width="100%">
                    <!-- Email Body -->
                    <tr>
                        <td cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="email-body" style="background-color: #FFFFFF; border-bottom: 1px solid #EDEFF2; border-radius: 5px; border-top: 1px solid #EDEFF2; margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%; word-break: break-word;" width="100%">
                            <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="email-body_inner" style="background-color: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 5px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0; width: 570px;" width="570">
                                <!-- Body content -->
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="content-cell" style="padding: 35px; word-break: break-word;">
                                        <table class="top-sub" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #EDEFF2; margin-bottom: 25px; padding-bottom: 25px; text-align: center; width: 100%;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="word-break: break-word;"><img alt="${sistema}" class="img-logo" src="http://sistemas.secad.to.gov.br/assets/img/portal_servidor.png" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto; width: 70px;" title="${sistema}" /> <span style="color: #78909c; display: block; font-size: 20px;">${sistema}</span></td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                        <h1 style="color: #2F3133; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0; text-align: left;">Olá ${nome},</h1>
                                        <p style="color: #74787E; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; text-align: left;"> Você solicitou uma <strong>recuperação de senha</strong>. <br />Clique no botão abaixo para alterar sua senha de acesso ao ${sistema}. </p>
                                        <!-- Action -->
                                        <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="body-action" style="margin: 30px auto; padding: 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;" width="100%">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td align="center" style="word-break: break-word;">
                                                    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td align="center" style="word-break: break-word;">
                                                                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                                                    <tr>
                                                                        <td style="word-break: break-word;"><a class="button button--blue" href="${recuperarSenhaUrl}" style="background-color: #017cc2; border-bottom: 10px solid #017cc2; border-left: 18px solid #017cc2; border-radius: 3px; border-right: 18px solid #017cc2; border-top: 10px solid #017cc2; box-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16); color: #FFF; display: inline-block; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">Alterar senha</a></td>
                                                                    </tr>
                                                                </table>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </table>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                        <p style="color: #74787E; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; text-align: left;">Caso não tenha feito essa solicitação, por favor, desconsidere este e-mail.</p>
                                        <p style="color: #74787E; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; text-align: left;">Atenciosamente, <br />Equipe DITEC/GESIS. </p>
                                        <!-- Sub copy -->
                                        <table class="body-sub" style="border-top: 1px solid #EDEFF2; margin-top: 25px; padding-top: 25px;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="word-break: break-word;">
                                                    <p class="sub" style="color: #74787E; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; text-align: left;">Caso você esteja com problemas com o botão acima, copie e cole o link abaixo em seu navegador web.</p>
                                                    <p class="sub" style="color: #74787E; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; text-align: left;">${recuperarSenhaUrl}</p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="word-break: break-word;">
                            <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="email-footer" style="margin: 0 auto; padding: 0; text-align: center; width: 570px;" width="570">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center" class="content-cell" style="padding: 35px; word-break: break-word;">
                                        <p class="sub align-center" style="color: #AEAEAE; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; text-align: center;">&copy; 2018 SECAD. Todos os Direitos Reservados.</p>
                                        <p class="sub align-center" style="color: #AEAEAE; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; text-align: center;"> Governo do Tocantins <br />Secretaria da Administração <br />(63) 3218-1500 </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
